| Issue | Severity | Fix |
|-------|----------|-----|
| No Authentication | CRITICAL | Implement JWT/OAuth2 |
| Hardcoded Secrets | CRITICAL | Use environment variables & secrets manager |
| No HTTPS | HIGH | Enforce TLS/SSL |
| No Input Validation | HIGH | Use validators & sanitizers |
| Missing Security Headers | HIGH | Add Helmet.js |
| No Rate Limiting | MEDIUM | Add express-rate-limit |
| No Error Handling | MEDIUM | Add global error handler |
| CORS Misconfiguration | MEDIUM | Restrict origins |
